## Install prerequisite libs

https://askubuntu.com/questions/1025350/sudo-usr-share-doc-libdvdread4-install-css-sh-command-not-found


sudo apt install libdvdcss2 libdvdread4 libdvdnav4 ubuntu-restricted-extras

or lubuntu-restricted-extras

sudo dpkg-reconfigure libdvd-pkg


## Install handbrake
https://handbrake.fr/docs/en/1.2.0/get-handbrake/download-and-install.html
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:stebbins/handbrake-releases
sudo apt-get update

sudo apt-get install handbrake-cli 

and handbrake-gtk if running a GUI



## Handbrake CLI

https://handbrake.fr/docs/en/latest/cli/command-line-reference.html



HandBrakeCLI -Z "Fast 1080p30" -i 

HandBrakeCLI -Z "Fast 1080p30" -i /media/dan/HILARY_AND_JACKIE --main-feature -o /home/dan/Media/Videos/JillaryJackie.m4v

sudo mount /dev/sr0 /media/cdrom
HandBrakeCLI -Z "HQ 1080p30 Surround" -i /media/cdrom --main-feature -o /home/dan/VideoRIPS/An_Education.m4v

